This folder contains the complete formalization of Polarity Theory, including:
- conceptual foundations  
- mathematical structure  
- cognitive dynamics  
- operator interactions  
- real‑world examples  
- visual diagrams  

Polarity Theory is the first and most essential component of the Theory Layer.  
It provides the structural backbone for all subsequent theories in the cognitive architecture.
